I am a huge 'Angry Birds' fan. 'Piggy Tales - Season 02' made me laugh a lot.
The Pigs do crazy construction stuff on this DVD. This DVD is the best.
It plays the videos as expected, compilation of all the web clips.  So if you like those and want them on a DVD, well say no more.
My son loves piggy and this was a great addition  to his collection.
Funniest video I've ever seen! I loved every minute of it!!
